1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,754
I build ad slots in my app because I hate ads.
我在自己的 App 里做广告位，因为我讨厌广告。

2
00:00:03,439 --> 00:00:05,850
Yup, I know how that sounds, so let me explain.
是的，我知道这话听着像什么，所以让我解释一下。

3
00:00:06,830 --> 00:00:11,870
I could've made DirtBikeX full of flyers and banners, and honestly, that'd be the easy way out.
我本可以把 DirtBikeX 做得满是传单和横幅广告，说实话，那才是最省事的做法。

4
00:00:12,020 --> 00:00:16,745
But I hate ads so much that I literally look away or close my eyes so that they don't get into my head
但我太讨厌广告了，以至于我真的会把目光移开或者闭上眼睛，不让它们进到我脑子里

5
00:00:16,900 --> 00:00:21,685
And I definitely want no riders opening my app and feel like they walked into a damn billboard.
而且我绝对不希望有骑手打开我的 App，感觉像是走进了一块该死的广告牌。

6
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:27,533
So these slots work differently. There are limited passes for real riders who actually belong in the sport.
所以这些广告位的运作方式不一样。有数量有限的通行证，留给真正属于这项运动的真实骑手。

7
00:00:27,733 --> 00:00:30,474
Here, you can go to the Sponsorship page and pick your spots.
在这里，你可以进入赞助页面，挑选你的位置。

8
00:00:30,961 --> 00:00:35,172
Choose when it starts, choose how long it runs, and DirtBikeX got you covered.
选择开始时间，选择投放时长，剩下的 DirtBikeX 都帮你搞定。

9
00:00:35,375 --> 00:00:40,415
Then, your profile will show up in multiple places across the app where people are actively looking
然后，你的个人主页会出现在 App 里的多个位置，正好是大家在主动寻找的地方

10
00:00:40,570 --> 00:00:46,613
And the biggest one is the splash screen, where users can pause it, tap your face, and go straight into your profile.
其中最大的一个是启动页，用户可以把它暂停，点一下你的脸，直接进入你的个人主页。

11
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:52,686
And don't worry, to keep it fair, passes are capped and rotated, so nobody gets to flood the scene.
别担心，为了保证公平，通行证有数量上限并且会轮换，所以没人能淹没整个圈子。

12
00:00:52,891 --> 00:00:55,332
And you even get to check your sponsorship stats too.
而且你还能查看自己的赞助数据。

13
00:00:55,947 --> 00:00:58,892
Regional exposure, daily trends, you name it.
区域曝光、每日趋势，应有尽有。

14
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:02,122
So essentially, it's a fair way to get seen by the right people.
所以本质上，这是一种公平的方式，让对的人看见你。

15
00:01:02,917 --> 00:01:05,627
My name is Rubio, and I'm giving out day passes for free.
我叫鲁比奥，我在免费送出单日通行证。

16
00:01:06,213 --> 00:01:08,333
Comment "PASS", and I'll see you in the app.
评论 “PASS”，我们 App 里见。
